---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="Regions - Bloom | IEZ Territories & Faction Control" 
    description="Navigate the dangerous territories of Terminal Grounds: The Dead Sky IEZ, Metro System, Machine Grave, Tech Wastes, Sump Gardens, and Security Checkpoints with dynamic faction control."
    keywords="Bloom regions, IEZ territories, Dead Sky, Metro System, Machine Grave, Tech Wastes, faction control, Terminal Grounds map"
    ogImage="/assets/images/renders/hero-wastes.png"
    type="website">
    
    <main class="regions-page">
        <section class="hero-regions quantum-grid py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container relative z-10">
                <div class="regions-header text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="holographic-text text-6xl md:text-8xl font-display font-black mb-6">Regions of the Terminal Grounds</h1>
                    <p class="regions-subtitle text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">Navigate the contested territories of post-Cascade Bloom</p>
                    <div class="glass-morphism-advanced inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-xl">
                        <span class="text-primary font-display font-bold text-lg">200km Interdiction Zone</span>
                        <span class="text-text-muted mx-4">•</span>
                        <span class="text-secondary font-semibold">6 Major Regions</span>
                        <span class="text-text-muted mx-4">•</span>
                        <span class="text-accent-cyan font-semibold">Dynamic Control</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="regions-overview py-20">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="holographic-text text-4xl font-display font-bold text-center mb-16">Key Territories</h2>
                
                <div class="regions-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="region-card iez interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced overflow-hidden hover:shadow-glow">
                        <div class="region-header flex justify-between items-start p-6 pb-0">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary">The Dead Sky (IEZ)</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level high bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Extreme Risk</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-image relative h-48 mx-6 mb-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
                            <img src="/assets/images/environments/iez-facility-clean.png" alt="IEZ Facility" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-bg-primary/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-content px-6 pb-6">
                            <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">The epicenter of the Cascade. A 200km radius where reality itself became unstable. Few who enter return unchanged, but the artifacts found here are beyond measure.</p>
                            <div class="region-details flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                <span class="detail-tag bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Monolith Phenomena</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Reality Distortion</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag bg-accent-cyan/20 text-accent-cyan px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Harvester Wrecks</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card metro">
                        <div class="region-header">
                            <h3>Metro System</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level variable">Variable Control</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-image">
                            <img src="/assets/images/environments/metro-corridor-premium.png" alt="Metro Corridor" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-content">
                            <p>Underground transit networks that still function. Faction control shifts daily. The safest routes for extraction—if you know who controls them.</p>
                            <div class="region-details">
                                <span class="detail-tag">Transit Network</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Dynamic Control</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Safe Passage</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card machine-grave">
                        <div class="region-header">
                            <h3>Machine Grave</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level contested">Contested</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-image">
                            <img src="/assets/images/environments/research-lab-clean.png" alt="Machine Grave" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-content">
                            <p>Semi-autonomous factories that still produce. Controlled jointly by Corporate Hegemony and Archive Keepers, these industrial complexes are vital to post-Cascade survival.</p>
                            <div class="region-details">
                                <span class="detail-tag">Industrial</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Factory Control</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Production</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card tech-wastes">
                        <div class="region-header">
                            <h3>Tech Wastes</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level scavenger">Scavenger Territory</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-image">
                            <img src="/assets/images/environments/tech-wastes-gritty.png" alt="Tech Wastes" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-content">
                            <p>Post-industrial wasteland where technology goes to die—and be reborn. Iron Scavengers rule here, salvaging Harvester technology for those who can pay.</p>
                            <div class="region-details">
                                <span class="detail-tag">Salvage Zone</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Artifact Trade</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Iron Scavenger Control</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card underground">
                        <div class="region-header">
                            <h3>Sump Gardens</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level safe">Civilian Safe Zone</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-image">
                            <img src="/assets/images/environments/underground-bunker-gritty.png" alt="Underground Bunker" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-content">
                            <p>Underground civilian settlements protected by the Civic Wardens. The closest thing to safety in the Terminal Grounds.</p>
                            <div class="region-details">
                                <span class="detail-tag">Civilian Protection</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Civic Warden Control</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Safe Haven</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card security">
                        <div class="region-header">
                            <h3>Security Checkpoints</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level directorate">Directorate Control</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-image">
                            <img src="/assets/images/environments/security-checkpoint-clean.png" alt="Security Checkpoint" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <div class="region-content">
                            <p>Military installation checkpoints controlled by the Sky Bastion Directorate. Order through discipline.</p>
                            <div class="region-details">
                                <span class="detail-tag">Military Control</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Order</span>
                                <span class="detail-tag">Directorate Territory</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="region-mechanics">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Regional Mechanics</h2>
                
                <div class="mechanics-grid">
                    <div class="mechanic-card">
                        <h3>Dynamic Control</h3>
                        <p>Faction control of regions shifts based on territorial warfare outcomes. Yesterday's safe passage may be today's battleground.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mechanic-card">
                        <h3>Extraction Routes</h3>
                        <p>Each region offers different extraction opportunities and challenges. Risk scales with potential rewards.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mechanic-card">
                        <h3>Environmental Hazards</h3>
                        <p>Cascade effects create unique hazards in each region, from reality distortions to automated defenses.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>